DataElement.preferredName: Negation Study Subject Administration, Management Performed Study Activity Identifier ISO21090.II.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The completed study level administrative activity that is independent of a study subject. EXAMPLE(S): IRB Approval, site enrollment, FDA audit. A unique symbol that establishes identity of an activity. EXAMPLE(S): 12345 is the identifier for a substance administration
